#: ../../C/Cancelmoose.rst:5
msgid "Cancelmoose[tm]"
msgstr "Cancelmoose[tm]"

#: ../../C/Cancelmoose.rst:7
msgid "/kan´sel·moos/"
msgstr "/kan´sel·moos/"

#: ../../C/Cancelmoose.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Usenet] The archetype and model of all good :ref:`spam`\\-fighters. Once "
"upon a time, the 'Moose would send out spam-cancels and then post notice "
"anonymously to :samp:`news.admin.policy`\\, :samp:`news.admin.misc`\\, and "
":samp:`alt.current-events.net-abuse`\\. The 'Moose stepped to the fore on "
"its own initiative, at a time (mid-1994) when spam-cancels were irregular "
"and disorganized, and behaved altogether admirably — fair, even-handed, and "
"quick to respond to comments and criticism, all without self-aggrandizement "
"or martyrdom. Cancelmoose[tm] quickly gained near-unanimous support from the"
" readership of all three above-mentioned groups."
msgstr ""
"[Usenet] すべての優れた\\ :ref:`spam`\\ "
"退治者の原型かつ模範。むかしむかし、'Mooseはスパムキャンセルを送出し、それから\\ :samp:`news.admin.policy`\\ 、\\"
" :samp:`news.admin.misc`\\ 、\\ :samp:`alt.current-events.net-abuse`\\ "
"に匿名で通知を投稿していました。'Mooseはスパムキャンセルが不規則で組織化されていなかった時期(1994年半ば)に自らの主導で前面に立ち、総じて見事に振る舞いました——公平で、公明正大で、コメントや批判への対応が早く、しかも自己宣伝や殉教者ぶりがまったくありませんでした。Cancelmoose[tm]は上記3つのグループすべての読者からほぼ満場一致の支持をすぐに獲得しました。"

#: ../../C/Cancelmoose.rst:14
msgid ""
"Nobody knows who Cancelmoose[tm] really is, and there aren't even any good "
"rumors. However, the 'Moose now has an e-mail address (<moose@cm.org>) and a"
" web site (`http://www.cm.org/ <http://www.cm.org/>`_.) By early 1995, "
"others had stepped into the spam-cancel business, and appeared to be "
"comporting themselves well, after the 'Moose's manner. The 'Moose has now "
"gotten out of the business, and is more interested in ending spam (and "
"cancels) entirely."
msgstr ""
"Cancelmoose[tm]が本当は誰なのかは誰も知らず、まともな噂すらありません。しかし'Mooseは今やeメールアドレス(<moose@cm.org>)とウェブサイト(`http://www.cm.org/"
" "
"<http://www.cm.org/>`_)を持っています。1995年初頭までに、他の者たちもスパムキャンセル業に乗り出し、'Mooseのやり方にならって立派に振る舞っているように見えました。'Mooseは今やこの業から手を引き、スパム(とキャンセル)を完全になくすことにより関心を持っています。"
